// Configuration settings file format documentation:
// https://help.apple.com/xcode/#/dev745c5c974
//
// Real Config*.xcconfig files are gitignored because they contain provider keys.
// For local development, copy Config-Development.xcconfig.template to
// Config-Development.xcconfig, fill it in, then set Config.xcconfig to include it:
//
// #include "Config-Development.xcconfig"
//
// For release builds, copy Config-Production.xcconfig.template to
// Config-Production.xcconfig and include that file from Config.xcconfig.
